data.description: Take a look at this amazing, recently updated four-bedroom home that boasts a pleasant-sized yard with both a deck and patio area for entertaining. The property includes a detached two-car garage, with a new garage door opener and a great workshop area. There is also a sizable storage shed. The living room is well-lit and features a stunning accent wall, while the spacious kitchen overlooks the family room and comes with a wood-burning stove. The guest bathroom now has a new toilet, and the whole house has new paint throughout. The heating system is brand new and has been changed from a furnace to baseboard heating, and a new oven has been installed. The living room also features a new ceiling fan with a chandelier. With no HOA, there is plenty of room to park outside toys. Check out this property today!
